          "id": "8ea473cd074d939f0fcb151e008c04ff017bad00",
          "message": "Bump version to 0.9.6\n\nDocumentation update accompanying the fine-grained type-conversion feature\n(convert_dates/nulls/booleans/numbers, previously committed in b44eb36):\n- CHANGELOG.md: promote [Unreleased] to [0.9.6], reopen an empty Unreleased\n- docs/src/resources/changelog.md and README.md's Changelog section: new\n  condensed v0.9.6 entries\n- Version-pin examples (README, installation guide, jvm-api reference,\n  jvm/README) bumped to 0.9.6; left the one benchmark-measurement footnote\n  tagged v0.9.5 alone since those numbers weren't re-measured this release\n- src/builder.rs: gate the four Python-only config accessors behind\n  #[cfg(feature = \"python\")], fixing a dead_code warning in default builds\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
